When should we use a databasae??
      Anytime you want to store data anywhere
      
Difference between relational and non relational databases
      relational databases use columns and rows like a spreadsheet while non relational databases dont use rows or columns. It uses a different model for data storage
      
What are some of the datatypes in postgressql??
      characters, numericals, binaries, monetary
      we use them depending on what kind of data we want to add or access
      
